    "Note: We do not perform similar transformations on the en-NG subset due to the high API pricing at the time of writing.",
    "We consider the in-dialect fine-tuned model as a strong baseline, while cross-dialect models are weak baselines.",
    "We compare all baselines and LORDD with in-dialect fine-tuned models on en-US conversations, which serves as our skyline result.",
    "Tables 1 and 2 Table 3 compares the performance of LORDD with the baselines and the skyline.",
